<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sección de Características Profesional</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'industrial': {
                            200: '#e5e7eb',
                            300: '#d1d5db',
                            900: '#111827'
                        },
                        'primary': {
                            300: '#93c5fd',
                            400: '#60a5fa',
                            500: '#3b82f6',
                            600: '#2563eb',
                            700: '#1d4ed8'
                        }
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        'heading': ['system-ui', 'sans-serif']
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        /* Fondo claro sofisticado */
        .gradient-bg-light {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 30%, #f1f5f9 70%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        }

        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

<section class="py-20 gradient-bg-light text-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Geometric Pattern Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%);"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 relative z-10">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                ¿Por Qué Elegirnos?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Somos tu socio de confianza para estrategias personalizadas 
                construidas sobre años de experiencia
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/logro.png" alt="Experiencia" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Experiencia que resuelve
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Nuestro equipo multidisciplinario domina compras, calidad, producción y logística para enfrentar cualquier reto industrial.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/logistica.png" alt="Logística" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Suministro adaptado a tus retos
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    No solo vendemos productos, diseñamos estrategias a la medida que optimizan costos y procesos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/logistic.png" alt="Abastecimiento" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Abastecimiento sin fronteras
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Navegamos comercio exterior, aduanas y regulaciones para que tu operación sea ágil y sin sorpresas.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/transferencia-de-conocimiento.png" alt="Alianzas" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Alianzas estratégicas e innovación
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Trabajamos con fabricantes líderes para ofrecer acceso a las últimas innovaciones del mercado.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 5 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/tech-support.png" alt="Soporte" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Soporte Técnico
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Equipo de soporte técnico disponible 24/7 para garantizar el mejor servicio.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 6 -->
            <div class="text-center group card-hover">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/30 group-hover:shadow-primary-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <img src="/images/distribucion.png" alt="Distribución" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-2">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
                    Logística optimizada
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Coordinamos entregas desde múltiples proveedores con eficiencia, integrando transporte, aduanas y almacenamiento para que tu operación no se detenga.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Statistics -->
        <div class="relative">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center pt-8">
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20 shadow-lg group-hover:bg-white/90 group-hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-300">
                            23
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">
                            Años de Experiencia
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20 shadow-lg group-hover:bg-white/90 group-hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-300">
                            11
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">
                            Países Atendidos
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20 shadow-lg group-hover:bg-white/90 group-hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-300">
                            1000+
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">
                            Proyectos Completados
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20 shadow-lg group-hover:bg-white/90 group-hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-300">
                            24/7
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">
                            Soporte Técnico
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>